Mertesacker: &quot;We see a lot of young players, they have a good future, that's my opinion, but you need to develop them in a lot of areas.&quot;<br />
<br />
Mertesacker: &quot;To train &amp; travel with us, it's the big time for such a young group, but it's now up to them to resist pressure situations.&quot;

Inter Milan's president Erick Thohir has confirmed an interest in signing Mesut Ozil during the upcoming January transfer window.<br />
<br />
Erick Thohir: &quot;He (Ozil) is definitely one of those players we are looking at.&quot;
